  ID: Knight2
  Name: Tommaso
  Icon: {fileID: 1208347981, guid: b2407ce4cf73ad348aec15ba9990f7a1, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Arrow through the neck, choking on blood with every rattling
    breath.\n\nStory: Brother Tommaso, an aged monk who carried water to the thirsty,
    grips your wrist with surprising strength. His voice is a wet gargle, but you
    hear him insist that all he wanted was to serve God until peace came. Blood fills
    his throat before he can finish the prayer \u2014 his lips still moving silently
    as his grip fades.\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal: 5"
  slotNumber: 0
  requiredResource: Bandage
  requiredAmount: 5
